1
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,625
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,625 --> 00:00:12,180
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:18,373
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,373 --> 00:00:24,499
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,499 --> 00:00:30,820
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:36,006
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,006 --> 00:00:43,206
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,206 --> 00:00:48,330
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,330 --> 00:00:49,943
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,943 --> 00:00:55,506
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,506 --> 00:01:02,106
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,106 --> 00:01:08,002
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,002 --> 00:01:11,722
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,180
Gao Yang!

15
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,940
Did you win first place?

16
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:13,679
I'm asking you, did you win first place?

17
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:17,739
I'll take you to the hospital.

18
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,559
I'm asking you, did you win first place?

19
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:30,259
I did, I did. I'll take you to the hospital.

20
00:02:30,259 --> 00:02:33,600
Didn't I tell you to win first place? Why did you come back?

21
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,839
I'll take you to the hospital.

22
00:02:35,839 --> 00:02:39,799
Why did you come back? Don't you want to win first place?

23
00:02:39,799 --> 00:02:42,240
I'm not going to the hospital!

24
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:46,340
It's all my fault. It's all my fault.

25
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,670
[Mi Jia, Xiaowen. Sure win!]

26
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:54,159
Why aren't they here yet?

27
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,759
Exactly.

28
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,879
They're here!

29
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:02,280
Xiaowen!

30
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,800
Go, Xiaowen!

31
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:06,479
Go, Xiaowen, go!

32
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,879
That's not right.

33
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:10,639
Why is it Chen Sizhe?

34
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,599
Xiaowen! Xiao...

35
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:19,000
He's not the second place either.

36
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,120
Where's Xiaowen?

37
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,720
It's okay.

38
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:24,199
Go, Xiaowen!

39
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:26,520
Where is he?

40
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,360
Mi Jia!

41
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,199
I knew it's Mi Jia!

42
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:37,459
Go, Mi Jia!

43
00:03:37,459 --> 00:03:40,519
Jia, you're awesome!

44
00:03:40,519 --> 00:03:43,679
Mi Jia, go, go, go!

45
00:03:43,679 --> 00:03:45,659
Let's go.

46
00:03:56,919 --> 00:04:00,820
Students, let me ask you, is the champion of the men's group from the No.3 High School?

47
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,540
Is he named Ye Xiaowen?

48
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:04,740
I don't think so.

49
00:04:04,740 --> 00:04:06,579
No.

50
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:12,579
No.

51
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:20,040
Mr. Gao, something terrible happened!

52
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,000
What happened?

53
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,120
Gao Yang is in the hospital!

54
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:39,630
[Tieyuan City High School Long Distance Running Competition]
Go, Go!

55
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,720
Where are you going, kid?

56
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,199
You still need to get stitches!

57
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,160
What are you doing?

58
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:20,040
It's Dong Dawei. I'll go settle the score with him.

59
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,640
Stop it!

60
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:28,439
Look at yourself!

61
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:30,879
I just can't let this go! You're supposed to be the champion!

62
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,679
Go back!

63
00:05:33,539 --> 00:05:35,339
Gao Yang!

64
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:40,640
I don't want first place anymore.

65
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,060
Bear with it.

66
00:06:04,979 --> 00:06:07,420
You're a big boy. Why are you crying?

67
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:09,199
Be strong.

68
00:06:29,382 --> 00:06:42,910
[Episode 14: Keep the Sadness to Myself]

69
00:06:42,910 --> 00:06:47,630
[Tieyuan Municipal Hospital]

70
00:06:50,539 --> 00:06:52,800
- Gao Yang!
- Oh, my God!

71
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,600
Why is Gao Yang like this? What happened?

72
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,000
Does it really hurt?

73
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:59,179
Xiaowen, w-what happened? A-Are you okay?

74
00:06:59,179 --> 00:07:01,179
Take it easy.

75
00:07:01,179 --> 00:07:03,500
Come on.

76
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,900
What happened to you?

77
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,639
Xiaowen, what happened?

78
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,840
What's going on?

79
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,360
You're fine. It won't scar.

80
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:33,919
Why did we encounter something like that during the preliminaries?

81
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,459
A bunch of b*stards!

82
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:41,080
It's okay, let's forget about it. Let's eat. Let's eat.

83
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:10,280
Xiaowen, don't take the competition to heart. I...

84
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,559
Mr. Gao, I'm full.

85
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,879
Who is it?

86
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:35,360
Hello, Mr. Gao.

87
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,600
Why are you guys here?

88
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,759
We're here to visit Gao Yang.

89
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:40,020
- Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang, we're here!

90
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,799
How are you feeling?

91
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:45,320
We bought you a bunch of snacks. There's canned food, fruits, and everything else.

92
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,360
Here are some pears.

93
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,840
How's your leg? Does it still hurt?

94
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:50,239
- Eat a pear.
- Give it to him later. He's having lunch.

95
00:09:50,239 --> 00:09:51,839
- It's so sweet.
- Don't start it.

96
00:09:51,839 --> 00:09:53,799
Where's Xiaowen?

97
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,200
I'm fine.

98
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,360
You can go home now.

99
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,960
You're not eating anymore?

100
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,980
Eat a pear.

101
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:11,179
Where are you going?

102
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:20,040
Stop eating that. We bought it for Gao Yang.

103
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:50,459
What are you doing?

104
00:10:50,459 --> 00:10:52,280
Get on the bike!

105
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,140
I'm not angry at you.

106
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,120
I know.

107
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:15,140
Why do I always make mistakes?

108
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,720
Take care of your injuries first.

109
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:23,120
The past is in the past.

110
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:25,459
The past won't come back.

111
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:43,679
If you want, you can always get it back.

112
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:04,839
Let's go.

113
00:13:04,839 --> 00:13:12,319
Let's go dress your wounds.

114
00:13:12,319 --> 00:13:18,590
♫ The street is playing the movie in my brain ♫

115
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:25,490
♫ Seems like everyone can see me at this moment ♫

116
00:13:25,490 --> 00:13:31,330
♫ I want to quickly press the fast-forward button ♫

117
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,080
Where are the people who interrupted the competition?

118
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:58,039
They were all arrested. They're just a bunch of hooligans.

119
00:13:58,039 --> 00:14:01,819
They've been sentenced to serve three years in prison for intentional assault.

120
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:06,640
Xiaowen, I know you're upset.

121
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:09,239
Just vent it out. Don't hold it in, okay?

122
00:14:09,239 --> 00:14:11,960
Mr. Gao, I'm all right.

123
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,700
Well,

124
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:19,699
don't worry about your college tuition. I'll take care of that.

125
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:26,340
How's your injury?

126
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:28,040
I'll live.

127
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:33,120
Gao Yang, don't pull a long face. The police already upheld justice for you.

128
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,820
Besides...

129
00:14:35,879 --> 00:14:38,299
shouldn't Xiaowen be more upset about this?

130
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,780
Why are you still eating soup?

131
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,679
What?

132
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:46,220
I'm injured.

133
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:48,740
I'll heal faster if I drink more soup.

134
00:15:00,519 --> 00:15:03,759
Let me reiterate about your homework. Finish that problem soon.

135
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:05,919
After that, everyone writes an 800-word essay.

136
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:07,399
The topic is Sense and Sensibility.

137
00:15:07,399 --> 00:15:08,639
Zhao Jiabao, what's going on with you?

138
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:10,200
I don't know.

139
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,399
Don't complain. Do that again and I won't be sensible anymore.

140
00:15:12,399 --> 00:15:14,299
Class dismissed.

141
00:15:14,299 --> 00:15:16,080
Gao Yang, how's your leg?

142
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,680
I'm fine.

143
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:22,579
Gao Yang, even if you beat up Dong Dawei, it won't make any difference!

144
00:15:22,579 --> 00:15:23,320
Just stay out of it.

145
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:25,240
Enough, I don't even mind anymore!

146
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:27,120
Go back to class. Don't get involved!

147
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,820
Gao Yang!

148
00:15:32,459 --> 00:15:34,779
You came right on time.

149
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:39,100
I'm here to see Ye Xiaowen.

150
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,679
I'm sorry.

151
00:15:45,679 --> 00:15:47,479
Gao Yang!

152
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,600
Only one of us can walk out of here alive today.

153
00:15:53,699 --> 00:15:54,919
I'm sorry.

154
00:15:54,919 --> 00:15:58,479
- How do you have the audacity to apologize?
How can you say that?

155
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:02,120
Are those people your friends?

156
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:05,480
Do you know how important this competition is to Xiaowen?

157
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:08,020
He can't participate in the national competition anymore!

158
00:16:09,020 --> 00:16:10,920
I'm sorry.

159
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:15,020
You're still saying that? Can you give him his first place back?

160
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:26,060
What happened?

161
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:27,659
Nothing.

162
00:16:30,399 --> 00:16:32,779
Those people are not my friends.

163
00:16:32,779 --> 00:16:37,620
On the day of the competition, I originally wanted to warn you.

164
00:16:37,620 --> 00:16:39,660
But I didn't get there in time.

165
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,700
I won't explain anything.

166
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:46,319
I already made it clear with them.

167
00:16:46,319 --> 00:16:48,199
From now on,

168
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:51,280
no one will harass you again.

169
00:16:55,519 --> 00:16:57,019
I'm sorry.

170
00:17:02,968 --> 00:17:05,035
[Principal's Office]

171
00:17:11,559 --> 00:17:16,859
Old Jin, I think I'm losing my eyesight from overworking.

172
00:17:16,859 --> 00:17:20,480
I remember I wrote "cultivating 20 elite athletes".

173
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,970
Why did it become 30 now?

174
00:17:22,970 --> 00:17:25,740
[Cultivating 30 elite athletes...]

175
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:28,379
20 is not enough.

176
00:17:28,379 --> 00:17:30,559
I've already made my choices. Twenty it is.

177
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:31,559
Just add ten more.

178
00:17:31,559 --> 00:17:33,499
I can't find that many.

179
00:17:33,499 --> 00:17:38,140
Either you take 20 or you get zero.

180
00:17:38,140 --> 00:17:39,319
That's because you're too lazy.

181
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,920
You're unrealistic and overambitious.

182
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:43,140
That's enough. Just complain here.

183
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:46,440
When the reporters arrive later, don't be in this mood.

184
00:17:48,939 --> 00:17:52,339
No, Old Jin, I'm not joking with you.

185
00:17:52,339 --> 00:17:56,820
This is not scientific. Do you think it's that easy to cultivate athletes?

186
00:17:58,160 --> 00:18:03,940
But you're Gao Bin, the first college graduate in our school's PE department.

187
00:18:04,580 --> 00:18:06,380
That's very scientific.

188
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:11,219
I'm going to receive the reporters. Do your best when they come later.

189
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:21,599
Let's go get some food.

190
00:18:22,979 --> 00:18:25,200
I don't want to. You go ahead.

191
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:30,440
Dong Dawei already apologized.

192
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:32,119
Just let it go.

193
00:18:32,119 --> 00:18:34,300
It has nothing to do with him.

194
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:37,120
It has something to do with me.

195
00:18:52,650 --> 00:18:54,259
Gao Yang,

196
00:18:55,279 --> 00:18:57,039
I've never blamed you for it.

197
00:18:57,039 --> 00:18:58,539
Say no more.

198
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:01,200
Let me be alone for a while.

199
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:30,279
What do you think? Do you want to go?
[Tieyuan Carnival: Tieyuan Night Fair, Shockingly Lively]

200
00:19:30,279 --> 00:19:34,659
You heartless woman. How can you still go to the night fair?

201
00:19:34,659 --> 00:19:37,499
Beibei is just trying to make Gao Yang and Xiaowen happy.

202
00:19:37,499 --> 00:19:39,039
- Well...
- Exactly.

203
00:19:39,039 --> 00:19:40,879
You don't know anything.

204
00:19:40,879 --> 00:19:44,180
What do you think, Jia? Would Xiaowen go?

205
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:48,999
I don't know. This competition is v-very important to him.

206
00:19:48,999 --> 00:19:52,999
I don't know what he's thinking right now.

207
00:19:52,999 --> 00:19:55,759
What should we do?

208
00:19:55,759 --> 00:19:59,500
Xiaowen didn't get first place and Gao Yang thinks it's all his fault.

209
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:02,419
The two of them are so depressed at home.

210
00:20:02,519 --> 00:20:05,540
I wouldn't even dare go to Mr. Gao's place now.

211
00:20:07,210 --> 00:20:08,759
Xiaowen.

212
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:13,139
Xiaowen, where's Gao Yang? He's not eating?

213
00:20:13,139 --> 00:20:15,000
He...

214
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:18,119
I'll bring some back for him.

215
00:20:18,119 --> 00:20:20,580
Is he still upset?

216
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:29,700
How about this, Xiaowen? I'll give you advice. You should smack him.

217
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:30,920
What are you saying, Zhao Jiabao?

218
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:33,279
You don't understand. Gao Yang brought those people there.

219
00:20:33,279 --> 00:20:37,240
He must think if he didn't get involved, Xiaowen would certainly win first place.

220
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,759
But his leg barely recovered.

221
00:20:39,759 --> 00:20:44,160
Beibei, don't be in a hurry to protect him. I think Jiabao is right this time.

222
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:50,700
You see, Gao Yang is such a stubborn person. If you don't smack him, would he be able to sleep?

223
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:54,599
Do we really need to beat him up?

224
00:20:54,599 --> 00:20:56,960
Why should I smack him?

225
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:00,719
I never blamed him for it.

226
00:21:00,719 --> 00:21:04,459
Xiaowen, just be bold and beat him up.

227
00:21:04,459 --> 00:21:07,880
I know him very well. He just needs to be smacked around.

228
00:21:09,079 --> 00:21:11,540
Be gentle with him.

229
00:21:14,839 --> 00:21:18,059
You guys keep eating. I'll bring the food to him.

230
00:22:04,930 --> 00:22:06,739
Drink some soda.

231
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:14,460
I brought you chicken drumsticks with rice.

232
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,860
If you keep doing this, I'll smack you.

233
00:22:22,519 --> 00:22:24,559
Come on, do it.

234
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:38,780
What do you mean? Why aren't you smacking me?

235
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:40,340
So childish.

236
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:42,440
What do you mean childish?

237
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:44,259
I don't want to smack you.

238
00:22:46,100 --> 00:22:47,700
Thank you.

239
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:55,840
Are you being sarcastic?

240
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:57,760
I mean it.

241
00:22:58,620 --> 00:23:01,599
Even if you brought those people there,

242
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:04,880
even if you really made a mistake,

243
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:07,399
I still won't blame you.

244
00:23:08,599 --> 00:23:10,499
Thank you

245
00:23:10,499 --> 00:23:12,559
for protecting me.

246
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,580
You're so boring.

247
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:21,039
You woke up early to train every day just to win this competition.

248
00:23:23,839 --> 00:23:28,680
If you forgive me so easily now, what about all the efforts you made before?

249
00:23:32,799 --> 00:23:34,739
What can I do?

250
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:41,040
A lot of things are unfair.

251
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:45,840
I chose to work hard,

252
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:48,839
but working hard doesn't always pay off.

253
00:23:51,799 --> 00:23:56,859
When something bad happens, there's no use complaining about it.

254
00:23:57,519 --> 00:23:59,979
I'll just learn to accept it.

255
00:24:02,039 --> 00:24:03,939
I won't accept it!

256
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:17,719
Have some tea.

257
00:24:17,719 --> 00:24:19,319
Let me introduce you.

258
00:24:19,319 --> 00:24:23,359
This is a senior reporter from our Tieyuan TV Station,

259
00:24:23,359 --> 00:24:25,659
Reporter Niu.

260
00:24:25,659 --> 00:24:31,399
We must count on him to promote our pre-Olympic track and field team.

261
00:24:34,219 --> 00:24:39,819
With the state of Tieyuan, he does have to listen to me if you want the video to have the feel of a metropolitan city.

262
00:24:39,819 --> 00:24:42,020
That's for sure.

263
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,559
This is...

264
00:24:46,559 --> 00:24:47,839
Let me introduce him.

265
00:24:47,839 --> 00:24:52,059
This is the coach of our track and field team, Gao Bin.

266
00:24:52,059 --> 00:24:54,759
Reporter Niu, hello.

267
00:25:10,039 --> 00:25:12,620
Don't you have another outfit?

268
00:25:17,970 --> 00:25:19,879
No.

269
00:25:19,879 --> 00:25:21,900
Well, borrow one then.

270
00:25:25,599 --> 00:25:28,760
Reporter, Niu, that's not necessary, right?

271
00:25:28,760 --> 00:25:34,200
We're a pre-Olympic track and field team, not a pre-Olympic model team.

272
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:50,440
Mr. Gao, just cooperate with Reporter Niu the best we can.

273
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:53,419
We're all trying to bring honor to the school.

274
00:25:57,319 --> 00:26:01,800
By the way, Reporter Niu, look at this. This is the information on our track and field team.

275
00:26:01,800 --> 00:26:03,580
Please take a look.

276
00:26:08,119 --> 00:26:12,219
This information seems to be put together

277
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:16,580
rather informally.

278
00:26:17,699 --> 00:26:19,940
- What's his name again?
- Gao Bin.

279
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:21,520
Gao Bin,

280
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:24,460
a second-rate teacher.

281
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:26,919
He's not a first-rate teacher?

282
00:26:26,919 --> 00:26:32,380
Participant of the 1st National University Games.

283
00:26:32,380 --> 00:26:33,480
What place did you get?

284
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:36,300
I didn't get any. I strained my leg.

285
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:42,880
Well, is he good enough to coach the pre-Olympic track and field team?

286
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,920
About that,

287
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:47,920
I...

288
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:51,100
Mr. Gao. Gao Bin!

289
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:52,240
I'm not doing this interview.

290
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:54,860
Why not? What did you promise me?

291
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:58,119
I promised you I would coach the team. I didn't agree to these.

292
00:26:58,119 --> 00:27:01,740
- I'm doing promotions for your own good, right?
- It's for your own good!

293
00:27:01,740 --> 00:27:03,359
Hello, Principal Jin.

294
00:27:07,450 --> 00:27:09,419
You're so ungrateful.

295
00:27:09,419 --> 00:27:12,459
Don't you know why I let you coach the team?

296
00:27:12,459 --> 00:27:17,860
You have two sons to raise. Is that little wage of yours enough to raise them?

297
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:22,900
That's why I let you coach the team.

298
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:27,880
If you have good results and get approved for your professional title, wouldn't you earn more money then?

299
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:31,260
Are you feeling sorry for me?

300
00:27:31,260 --> 00:27:34,220
You asked me to coach the team because you felt sorry for me and not because of my abilities, right?

301
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:37,980
- I just want you to earn more money.
- I have money!

302
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:40,379
Yeah, right.

303
00:27:40,379 --> 00:27:42,360
Sure, I don't have anything.

304
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:45,820
But I have integrity. I won't be the coach anymore!

305
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:50,299
You! Gao Bin. Gao Bin!

306
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:55,300
What the heck?

307
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:03,340
Xiaowen, are you sure you're okay?

308
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:06,260
What could be wrong with me?

309
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:10,720
If you can't compete in the national competition, you won't get the tuition waiver.

310
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:14,439
You won't be able to... go to the Beijing University of Technology.

311
00:28:15,799 --> 00:28:20,319
The chance to get the tuition waiver was a surprise anyway. It's good that you seized the chance.

312
00:28:20,319 --> 00:28:21,799
Don't take it lightly.

313
00:28:21,799 --> 00:28:25,120
You still need to pass the admission requirement on the college entrance exam, understand?

314
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:29,219
The tuition for the Beijing University of Technology is really expensive. What are you going to do?

315
00:28:31,970 --> 00:28:33,779
I have my ways.

316
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:40,240
Don't tell anyone about this, especially Gao Yang.

317
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:46,499
Please check out the Tieyuan Night Fair. There's food, drinks, and fun activities there. Check it out. Thank you.
[Tieyuan Night Fair]

318
00:28:46,499 --> 00:28:49,480
Beibei originally wanted to take us there.

319
00:28:50,491 --> 00:28:52,264
[Tieyuan Carnival: Tieyuan Night Fair, Shockingly Lively]

320
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:04,860
Xiaowen, let me do it.

321
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:08,400
It's okay, Mr. Gao. Go take a break.

322
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:13,419
You're a child. It's not right to let you cook for us all the time.

323
00:29:13,419 --> 00:29:15,439
I'm supposed to do that as an adult.

324
00:29:15,439 --> 00:29:18,939
You're so busy with work every day. This is what I should do.

325
00:29:22,739 --> 00:29:26,800
Xiaowen, you really are a good boy.

326
00:29:27,540 --> 00:29:29,240
However,

327
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:35,040
you have to learn to be a child sometimes.

328
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:46,659
Actually, what I mean to say is, it's all right if you win first place or not.

329
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:53,740
Don't feel stressed about going to college and picking a major.

330
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:56,410
I can handle the tuition and everything else.

331
00:29:57,860 --> 00:30:01,350
From now on, you can go anywhere you want.

332
00:30:02,170 --> 00:30:04,480
Don't make yourself suffer.

333
00:30:10,970 --> 00:30:14,859
The soup is almost ready. I'll tell Gao Yang that dinner is ready.

334
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:21,140
Gao Yang, dinner is ready.

335
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:25,520
What sweepstakes can they have at the night fair? Those are all scams. You guys go ahead.

336
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:29,700
Look at you, the competition has been over for 2 weeks. Can you be a man?

337
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,599
If you keep this up, I'll smack you.

338
00:30:31,599 --> 00:30:34,379
Come downstairs and smack me then. Over!

339
00:30:41,079 --> 00:30:43,659
Beibei asked you to go to the night fair?

340
00:30:44,599 --> 00:30:46,299
I don't want to go.

341
00:30:47,119 --> 00:30:50,740
Gao Yang, do you think I can't do anything about you?

342
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:53,279
Wait, why are you here? How many times have I told you?

343
00:30:53,279 --> 00:30:54,680
Don't just walk into the men's room.

344
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:57,559
I don't care! I'll smack you today!

345
00:30:57,559 --> 00:31:01,360
Let go of me, Xiaowen. Stay out of this! I'm telling you, I hate to see men like this! Get over here!

346
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:02,720
What do you want? You're crazy!

347
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:05,000
Aren't you feeling guilty towards him? Well, treat him nicer, then!

348
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,519
Don't just keep whining every day! Are you a man or not?

349
00:31:07,519 --> 00:31:10,039
- Beibei,
- Let go of me! You can't beat him up, right?

350
00:31:10,039 --> 00:31:12,440
Let me do it! Get over here!

351
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:15,700
You're so... Give it back! Give it to me!

352
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:19,180
I won't! I usually let you win. If you keep this up, I'll fight back!

353
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:21,940
- Come on, then! Am I scared of you? Give it to me!
- No, I won't!

354
00:31:21,940 --> 00:31:24,759
Gao Yang, you're asking for a beating! Let go!

355
00:31:24,759 --> 00:31:26,559
Enough!

356
00:31:34,559 --> 00:31:37,839
Beibei, let's go to the night fair.

357
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:43,900
Wait for me.

358
00:31:57,010 --> 00:31:59,960
Tieyuan Carnival, here we come!

359
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,279
We're here!

360
00:32:01,279 --> 00:32:03,200
We are the S

361
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,119
H

362
00:32:04,119 --> 00:32:05,819
E of Tieyuan!
(T/N: S.H.E is a famous Taiwanese girl group)

363
00:32:05,819 --> 00:32:07,520
Count me in!

364
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:09,340
Go play with the boys.

365
00:32:09,340 --> 00:32:11,440
Let's go over there!

366
00:32:12,179 --> 00:32:15,980
We... we're the Little Tigers of Tieyuan!
(T/N: a Taiwanese boy band)

367
00:32:17,259 --> 00:32:18,519
Gao Yang,

368
00:32:18,519 --> 00:32:21,720
will you stop pulling a long face? Aren't we here for fun?

369
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:24,080
You guys go ahead. So childish.

370
00:32:25,979 --> 00:32:30,119
Xiaowen, let's go have fun. We can go play the shooting game.

371
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,697
[Welcome]

372
00:32:36,599 --> 00:32:38,299
Nice shot!

373
00:32:38,979 --> 00:32:41,840
Come on Bin. You're here alone? Where's Old Jin?

374
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,680
Which Old Jin?

375
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:48,100
That Old Jin. Principal Jin, share a table with Bin.

376
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:53,040
I'm not sharing with him. I'll sit by myself.

377
00:33:01,799 --> 00:33:04,100
Nice shot!

378
00:33:04,100 --> 00:33:09,680
Nice shots require a nice coach. He seems so professional.

379
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:14,019
He certainly won't leave the team halfway through the game.

380
00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:21,020
Look at the image of that coach. You can tell he cares about the interests of the whole.

381
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:24,719
He would take interviews and put on makeup when he is asked to.

382
00:33:24,719 --> 00:33:26,920
It's just a TV interview.

383
00:33:27,559 --> 00:33:29,019
What's the big deal?

384
00:33:29,019 --> 00:33:31,679
Jin Libin, what are you doing?

385
00:33:32,799 --> 00:33:35,079
I'm eating skewers. What am I doing?

386
00:33:35,079 --> 00:33:40,319
Did you eat sour pickles at lunch? Why are you mocking me with such all these "sour words"?
(T/N: "sour words" means sarcasm)

387
00:33:41,659 --> 00:33:44,260
So what if I'm mocking you?

388
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:16,606
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

389
00:34:16,606 --> 00:34:23,771
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

390
00:34:23,771 --> 00:34:29,861
♫ Starlight shines along the way ♫

391
00:34:29,861 --> 00:34:36,001
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

392
00:34:36,001 --> 00:34:42,653
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

393
00:34:42,653 --> 00:34:48,293
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

394
00:34:48,293 --> 00:34:52,106
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

395
00:34:52,106 --> 00:34:55,528
♫ Set sail for your dreams ♫

396
00:34:55,528 --> 00:34:58,823
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

397
00:34:58,823 --> 00:35:05,583
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

398
00:35:05,583 --> 00:35:08,794
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

399
00:35:08,794 --> 00:35:13,006
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

400
00:35:13,006 --> 00:35:16,826
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

401
00:35:16,826 --> 00:35:24,786
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
